snippet.title: MASQUERADE
snippet.description:
demo: https://doritoburrito.itch.io/masquerade

this isnt in development anymore in case anyone was wondering, it was scrapped around the start of 2021 because it was too ambitious and would have got caught in dev hell. the demo is still up to play, and a lot of the planned content and concepts for this will be reused in future projects.
